Kitutu Chache North MP Jimmy Angwenyi has been urged to address problems in allocation of bursaries to university students instead of politicising the issue.MP hopeful James Atandi yesterday said, &ldquo;Concerns over skewed allocation and delay of disbursement of bursaries should be addressed. I&rsquo;m advising Angwenyi to sit down with the students and sort these things out.&rdquo;